snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 21 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 21 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 8th March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

ta.title: எஸ் கே சார் ஓட கிளாஸ் | Finale - Karmyuddh | Watch in Hindi, Tamil or Telugu | The Viral Fever
ta.description:

இந்த ஹோலி எபிசோடில் உங்களை நாங்கள் ஆச்சரியப்படுகிறோம்!! இப்போதே last episode காக காத்திருங்கள்!

snippet.title: Chamkeela Angeelesi - Lyrical | Dasara | Nani, Keerthy Suresh | Santhosh Narayanan | Srikanth Odela
snippet.description:
Here is the peppy 'Chamkeela Angeelesi' from 'Dasara' (Telugu) starring Nani, Keerthy Suresh & Others. Directed by Srikanth Odela. A Santhosh Narayanan Musical

For more latest songs and videos, subscribe now @saregamasouth 

Song Credits:
Song: CHAMKEELA ANGEELESI
Lyrics: KASARLA SHYAM
Singer: RAM MIRIYALA, DHEE
Composed, Arranged and Programmed by Santhosh Narayanan
Violin: Embar S Kannan
Bass: Naveen Napier

Mandolin: Joseph Vijay

Recording Engineers: Pranav Muniraj, Rupendar Venkatesh

Future Tense Studios
Musicians Coordinator: Meenakshi Santhosh

Produced by Sudhakar Cherukuri on SLV Cinemas Banner

Producer: - Sudhakar Cherukuri
Music: - Santhosh Narayanan

Choreographer: Prem Rakshith
Editor: - Navin Nooli
Art: - Avinash Kolla
PRO: - Vamsi Shekar
Digital Marketing: First Show
Label: Saregama India Limited, A RPSG Group Company

Lyrics:
Chamkeela angeelesi O Vadhiney
Chaaku lekkundetodey O Vadhiney
Kandlaku ainaa betti kaththoley
Kannetla koduthundeney
Sinigina baneeneysi O Vadhiney
Nattintla koosuntadey O Vadhiney
Maasina lungi yesi ippudu
Manchamlaney pantadey

Pendlaina koththala aththarlu poosinney
Nee seera singhulu patti yenakenaka thiriginney
Muddhulisthundey poolu thesthundey
Sakkera lekka nee maatalumtundey
Maarey nee theeru perigey nee noru
Mandhukalavaataithiney

Kadupula intha bosi O Vadhiney
Koduthadey bandakesi O Vadhiney
Amavaasa punnaaniko atlatla
Akkaraku pakkakoththadammo

Kanta neeranna pettakunda santibidda lekka
Ninnu Aluguthuntey boodharakiyyaledhaa
Nuvvu seetiki maatiki gintha dhaanni ganthajeysi
Ijjathamtha bazaarlesthalevaa

Yem gaali sokeno…veenneththi thirigeno..
Paathabaddanemo chethanaitha ledho
Ultaa nannitla mandhi mungatla badhnaam jeththadu

Noridisi adagadhuraa baammardhi
Cheppindhi cheyyadhuraa baammardhi
Pakkintla koosuntadhi naa meedha
Chaadeelu chepthuntadhi
Naa gonthu kosindrantu bammardhi
Sokaalu peduthuntadhi bammardhi
Muchchatlu jeppabothey meeyakka
Moothantha thipputhuntadhi

Seekatla unnaa vaakitla unnaa
Kantiki reppoley kaasthadu mogadu
Yentha lollaina nuvventa untey
Yedhuru nilsi vaadu gelsi vasthaadu
Gosalni joostha unnaa yedhainaa
Gundella dhaasthaaduley
Nee bottu nee gaajuley yenthainaa
Vaani paanaaluley

Label: Saregama India Limited, A RPSG Group Company

snippet.title: Meeting में Jetha ने मारी सभी को पिचकारी | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Holi Special
snippet.description:
Jetha makes fun of Iyer as he is unable to understand Hindi. Jetha then asks Iyer to learn Hindi and Gujarati language, as it will be of great help to both of them. However, Iyer takes Jetha’s advice as an offence. The fight escalates and every member of Gokuldham Society then declares that they will speak in their respective language. As a result, the Undhiyu party gets cancelled.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast – Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Produced By – Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #SonyPAL #holi #holispecial #happyholi 

Subscribe to Sony Pal: http:/a/www.youtube.com/sonypalindia

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises

snippet.title: Best International Women's Day | Dreamz Unlimited
snippet.description:
International Women's Day (IWD) is a global day celebrating the social, economic, cultural and political achievements of women. The day also marks a call to action for accelerating gender parity.
Marked annually on March 8th, IWD is one of the most important days of the year to, celebrate women's achievements, educate and awareness raise for women's equality, call for positive change advancing women.

snippet.title: Gokuldham वाले खेलने लगे Ketchup और Besan से Holi! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Holi Special
snippet.description:
Popatlal tries to make fried snacks for the breakfast but he notices that he does not have any tomato sauce in the house to have with the snacks. So, he tries to call Abdul, but Abdul does not pick his phone up. Popatlal then comes out on the balcony of his house and shouts Abdul’s name. Bhide and others notice Popatlal shouting so they ask him the reason for his yelling. Popatlal tells everyone that he has made some fried snacks and he needs some tomato sauce to eat with them. Bhide tells Popatlal that he will give him the tomato sauce. Later, Bhide goes to Popatlal with a bottle of tomato sauce and leaves. When Popatlal notices that the tomato is expired he comes downstairs screaming Bhide’s name. What will Popatlal do now? Let’s find out.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast – Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Produced By – Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #SonyPAL #holi #holispecial #happyholi 

Subscribe to Sony Pal: http:/a/www.youtube.com/sonypalindia

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises

Watch all the 'Holi Special' clips especially curated for you:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G0mUUtCU8U1fh6FBZKC6ahg

snippet.title: Peshawar Zalmi vs Quetta Gladiators | Highlights | Pakistan Super League | 8th March 2023
snippet.description:
Peshawar Zalmi batted superbly and posted a mammoth total of 240 runs at the end of their innings. Captain Babar Azam was the star with a century to his name. Peshawar Zalmi looked like the winners even before Quetta Gladiators came to bat, however, Jason Roy had other plans. The opener looked unstoppable as he was dealing in boundaries and went on to make 145 runs from just 63 deliveries. This power-packed knock helped the Quetta Gladiators to win by 8 wickets and 10 balls remaining. 
.
.

snippet.title: Women Task Force | Purvi Gives A Tough Fight Against An 'Anaconda Man' | CID | 7 March 2023
snippet.description:
Purvi fought the case to save many people from a dangerous snake. The power of the snake was misused by people who took the lives of many people. Purvi with other officers gave a tough fight and helped them to save mankind.  Will team CID be successful in saving their lives? To know more watch the full episode.

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode No:  1339
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh
 
#CID #सीआईडी #CID2023 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #CID Nostalgia #LIVCrime #NewCID #LatestCID #Crime

Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIVJzesdfwktpj4U8HRY8p6k

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 22 Teaser - 8th March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 22 Teaser - 8th March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: Ittar - Jasmine Sandlas | BPraak | Jaani | Arvindr Khaira | Desi Melodies
snippet.description:
Desi Melodies is here with the hottest track of the season at the onset of summer, Ittar. Performed by Jasmine Sandlas, the vocal delivery is chilling with Jaani's lyrics that show off the love for her partner over BPraak’s modern-folk composition complemented by the man behind the lens, Arinvdr Khaira. 

This Punjabi banger is all about the Gulabi Queen’s mesmerizing voice taking the centerstage to talk about how she wants to adorn herself with the fragrance of ‘Ittar’ (a traditional Indian perfume) and spread it in every inch of her body so that her love can feel her presence even when she's not there. 

Full of metaphors that highlight the depth of romance, Sandlas touches upon the idea of fate and how they’re destined to be together. The combination of Jaani's layered writing, BPraak's exquisite music, and Arvindr Khaira’s inimitable visual storytelling; this musical bouquet is exactly how Jasmine concludes - “If Ittar had a sound, this would be it."

Listen to ‘Ittar’ on your favourite streaming platform - https://bit.ly/Jasmine_Sandlas_Ittar

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3713 - 8 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3713: Tapu Sena Ke Holi Plans
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide and other members of the Gokhuldham members are worried about the notorious plans of Tapu Sena on the occasion of Holi. Bhide tells about his dilemma to everyone, and Jethalal assures them that Tapu will not be doing anything naughty. Tapua also assures everyone that they will not disturb anyone during the festival. Iyer discusses his worry as last year he was painted with colours, Babita advises him that they will be testing the colours before applying them. Stay Tuned

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3713, 8 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000212642

Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Jetha ने मारा Auto में बैठने से पहले Bhide को धक्का | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Holi Special
snippet.description:
Like always, Jethalal shows up late at the meeting held in the Club House. As Iyer suggests that Jethalala should be banned from society meetings, Jethalal starts playing Holi with water guns, beginning with Iyer. Later, after a lot of fun and enjoyment, the meeting starts where Iyer and Popatlal announce that there won’t be any Holi celebrations this year in Gokuldham.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast – Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Produced By – Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #SonyPAL #holi #holispecial #happyholi 

Subscribe to Sony Pal: http:/a/www.youtube.com/sonypalindia

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises

Watch all the 'Holi Special' clips especially curated for you:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G0mUUtCU8U1fh6FBZKC6ahg

snippet.title: Qalandar Episode 42 - [Eng Sub] - Muneeb Butt - Komal Meer - Ali Abbas - 4th Mar 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Qalandar Episode 42 - [Eng Sub] - Muneeb Butt - Komal Meer - Ali Abbas - Hiba Aziz - 4th March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Qalandar is a story of a girl’s firm belief in her God and His decisions while the rest of the world continues to hurt, defame and challenge her.

Dur-e-Adan is a young and innocent girl who has grown up under the care of her uncle and aunt. Despite being an orphan at an early age, Dur-e-Adan doesn’t complain about her challenges and difficulties.

On the contrary, Tabriz is a handsome young man who aspires to achieve great things in life. Living in the same locality, Tabriz’s parents find Dur-e-Adan suitable for him as a life partner. However, Tabriz’s life takes a surprising turn when Sumbul hailing from a wealthy family falls in love with him. In efforts to secure his future financially, Tabriz forgets the gift that he has been bestowed in the form of Dur-e-Adan for this world and hereafter. Soon, Tabriz’s half-heartedness and conflicting loyalties in the form of greed begins to reflect in his relationship with Dur-e-Adan.

Amidst all the atrocities faced by Dur-e-Adan will she continue to be patient with those around her? Will Tabriz realize the respect and love that Dur-e-Adan deserves or will he continue to hurt her? Will Tabriz be able to mend his relationship with Dur-e-Adan?

Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Head of Project: Mikaal Zulfiqar
Written By: Samra Bukhari
Directed By: Saima Waseem
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Muneeb Butt as Tabrez
Komal Meer as Dur-e-Adan
Ali Abbas as Irfan

Asma Abbas as Safiya

snippet.title: Nadiya Ke Paar Funny Scene | Best Scene Of Nadiya Ke Paar | Holi Special | Sachin Pilgaonkar
snippet.description:
Checkout this Classic Scene from the Classic Movie "Nadiya Ke Paar" released in the year 1982. Starring Sachin Pilgaonkar, Sadhana Singh, Inder Thakur, Savita Bajaj, Sheela David. Watch such classic scene only on @Rajshri 

#nadiyakepaar #bollywoodmovies #romanticmovie 

Synopsis-
The story is based on the first half of a Hindi novel, Kohbar Ki Shart by Keshav Prasad Mishra. A Brahman farmer from Eastern Uttar Pradesh lives with his two nephews. He falls ill and is treated by a Vaidya (indigenous medical practitioner) from another village. When the farmer feels okay, he asks the Vaidya about his fees. The Vaidya asks for the farmer's eldest nephew to marry his eldest daughter. The farmer readily agrees.

Omkar marries the Vaidya's elder daughter Roopa, and they start living happily. Roopa gives birth to a baby. During Roopa's pregnancy, her younger sister Gunja comes to live with her. While there, she falls in love with Omkar's younger brother Chandan.

Learning of their love, Roopa promises to help them marry. But, she dies in an accident; and nobody else knows about the love affair. The farmer and the Vaidya decide that Gunja should marry the widower Omkar, to take care of her sister's baby. But moments before the wedding rituals are completed, Chandan and Gunja's love affair is revealed. He is allowed to marry Gunja with everyone's consent.

The rural culture and languages of Uttar Pradesh are portrayed authentically in the film. The movie is based on the first half of the novel. It changes the partners in the second marriage, as the novel had the proposed marriage between Gunja and Omkar taking place. The novel proceeded with the development of their relationship, where Omkar dies of illness and eventually Gunja also dies leaving Chandan alone.

Nikah Episode 45 - [Eng Sub] - Haroon Shahid - Zainab Shabbir - 5th March 2023  - HAR PAL GEO

Nikah is a powerful and inspiring story of a young girl’s fight for her social and religious rights. 
Opinionated and confident by nature, Anusha is a beautiful young girl who knows how to stand up for her rights. After losing her mother at a young age, Anusha has been brought up by her aunt, Umaima with a lot of love and care. Umamia is a bit hesitant about Anusha’s assertiveness and often makes her understand. 
Class fellows and best friends, Anusha and Haris are in love with each other and soon plan to marry. On the contrary, Hamdaan is a handsome young man who belongs to a wealthy family and is the only son of his father. He falls in love with Anusha on his very first meeting with her however is respectful of Anusha’s choices.
Anusha’s hope and dreams come crashing down when Haris challenges her thoughts. The supposedly liberal fabric of Haris and his family is exposed when Anusha takes a stand for her rights. After losing everything, will Anusha stay true to herself and fight against all odds? Despite everything, will Anusha realize her true admirer and supporter in form of Hamdaan?

Writer: Nuzhat Saman
Director: Zahid Mehmood

snippet.title: இடியாப்ப அச்சி போதும் ! யார் வேணாலும் ஈஸியாக பரோட்டா செய்யலாம் | Easy Parrota Recipe Tamil | parotta
snippet.description:
#parottarecipeintamil, #layerparottaintamil #parotta

Easy Method of  Parotta making

350gram of Maida flour in the Bowl 
Add required salt ,one spoon oil and mixed well
Adding Boiled water little by little mixed well
make dough chapati consistency.
take idiyappam Achu and filled this batter 3/4
three spoons of cooking oil Grease with plate
make parotta peda shown in the video

cover it Rest in 15mins to 30mins
apply oil in top of peda
then gentle press  make parotta
 cooking parotta in the medium flame
Now your layered parotta is ready..

snippet.title: Rang Beranger Khela | রং বেরঙের খেলা | Best of Gopal 2022 | Holi Special
snippet.description:
দোলের  দিন এবার আর রং খেলা যাবে না কারণ বাজারে রঙের খুব অভাব কিন্তু রাজা সহ কেউই একথা মানতে রাজী না; তাই বৈজ্ঞানিক-এর ওপর দ্বায়িত্ব পরে আবির ও রং বানাবার। কিন্তু সহকারী হিসেবে আরও জনা  তিনেক লোক লাগবে কাজের জন্য। মন্ত্রী -র কুট চক্রান্তে নিয়োজিত লোকেরা কিভাৱে মুনাফার জাল বিছিয়েছিলো এই কাজ ঘিরে আর গোপাল কিভাবে সেই জাল ছিঁড়ে প্রমান করে মন্ত্রীর কারচুপি ও কারসাজি?

Show Name – Gopal Bhar
Episode No - 830

#gopalbhar #sonyaath #গোপালভাঁড় #bestofgopalbhar2022

Click here to Subscribe to SONY AATH Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBz9qbqujcjIavFmBJW2oZw?sub_confirmation=1

About Gopal Bhar:
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous, and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers.

Click to watch all the episodes of Best of Gopal 2022 - https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL5O3zv2ZcAShUXWjPDFfHkuRXVXSCqlAe

Watch Now - https://bit.ly/Varisuonprime

About:
Vijay, the prodigal son of business tycoon Rajendran agrees to take over the reins of the business, much to the chagrin of his brothers. About Prime Video
Prime Video is a premium streaming service that offers Prime members a collection of award-winning Amazon Original series, thousands of movies and TV shows—all with the ease of finding what they love to watch in one place.  Find out more at PrimeVideo.com.

Included with Prime Video: 
Thousands of acclaimed TV shows and movies across languages and geographies, including Indian films such as Jai Bhim, Shershaah, Toofaan, Sardar Udham, Coolie No. 1, Gulabo Sitabo, Shakuntala Devi, Sherni, Durgamati, Chhalaang, Hello Charlie, Cold Case, Narappa, Sara’s, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi and Tuck Jagadish, along with Indian-produced Amazon Original series like Mumbai Diaries 26/11, The Last Hour, Paatal Lok, Bandish Bandits, Breathe, Comicstaan Semma Comedy Pa, The Family Man, Mirzapur, Inside Edge and Made In Heaven. Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like The Tomorrow War, Coming 2 America, Cinderella, Borat Subsequent Moviefilm, Without Remorse, The Wheel of Time, American Gods, One Night in Miami, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Cruel Summer, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel and many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi and Bengali.

Instant Access: 
Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV and multiple gaming devices. Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid and post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices and tablets and watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.

Enhanced experiences
Make the most of every viewing with 4K Ultra HD- and High Dynamic Range (HDR)-compatible content. Go behind the scenes of your favourite movies and TV shows with exclusive X-Ray access, powered by IMDb. Save it for later with select mobile downloads for offline viewing.

Included with Prime
Prime Video is available in India at no extra cost with Prime membership for just ₹1499 annually or ₹179 monthly. New customers can find out more at www.amazon.in/prime and subscribe to a free 30-day trial.
